snippet.title: Sensible World of Soccer 95/96 gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Sensible World of Soccer 95/96 (aka SWOS 95/96), Dos PC game produced by Sensible Software in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/sensible-world-of-soccer-95-96/5084/
Playing world cup competition with Brasil. Eliminated at quarter of final by Belgium. Title incredibly won by Switzerland against Italy.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
